Δ𝑣 ≈ 0.5𝑣𝑡ℎ,𝑖 for ions. We use a velocity range for binning the
particles from −𝑐 to 𝑐 in each dimension for electrons and from
−0.4𝑐 to 0.4𝑐 for ions."
